{"tid":1430233,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲余文樂被爆背住老婆 返大陸東區摸奶！！！","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T11:39:59.000Z","uid":153051,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9858b12de5a92c6714b9a379db97729ecd96da3c","tid":1430233,"uid":153051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:40:08.000Z","msg":"講了兩篇台灣的政治故事。很多反送中的資訊，大家都能透過網路媒體去看到了。我來說說為什麼余文樂今天會在微博發文。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n余文樂篇<br />\n余文樂Shawn，娶了台灣太太Sarah王予柔（王棠雲），王棠雲爸爸叫做王東生，王東生經營國產皮件跟貿易起家。王東生把賺來的錢投資中國的房產，跟中國的開發商（台灣叫建商）一起炒房，結果被騙。於是台灣生意跳票，房子被法拍。<br />\n當初余文樂會娶她，有部分是因為他家有錢，另一部分是因為王東生在中國那邊經營的政商關係。<br />\n而余文樂的身份也很受王東生青睞。原因是余文樂背後的金主太陽城集團。<br />\n余文樂背後的金主，是太陽城集團，也就是港澳黑社會。太陽城集團在港珠澳地帶的角色，表面是飯店、賭場兼開發商，實際上，是幫忙中國政府洗錢的單位。<br />\n太陽城集團在澳門處理四種錢，第一種是詐騙集團資金，第二種是毒品交易，第三種不問來由的資金匯兌，第四種政商賄賂。<br />\n處理的手法我簡單講。今天小華跟小明有利益關係，小華想要把錢給小明，於是小華聯絡賭場，說他要拿1億給小明，交給賭場處理。於是小華把一億的現金加手續費「輸」給太陽城，然後小明再到VIP廳「贏」回1億囉。不管哪種大抵都是這樣處理的。<br />\n而王東生卡在中國的資金，想拿回來、必須依靠太陽城集團在中國的政商關係，太陽城集團的華哥（周焯華）是中南海集團的一員，也是廣東省政協，基本上不是國際事件，在華南幾乎就是橫著走。<br />\n而余文樂的Madness還有個人電競戰隊Madteam 投資背後的金主都係出太陽城集團。太陽城集團本來就是親中的組織，不但是黑社會，還是那種聰明的黑社會。懂得利用會計師跟律師處理法律跟金流問題。也很聰明的如果是大筆交易都是透過BVI處理。<br />\n我看了看我的勞力士，打開我的手機，正在思考著要不要打給阿樂。<br />\n我打給阿樂大部分都是剛好兩個都在台灣的時候，因為阿樂實在太愛去東區Zara樓上摸奶了。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93KJd2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93KJd2k.jpg&h=cad12ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f2a151e556c89af05cb4b30b0584d938aa2af6","tid":1430233,"uid":153051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:42:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9e924648b119e5cfa10842f9a52d48e1e1b8b980","tid":1430233,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41103acc303e77f7a07080bf6135bbc18719b774","tid":1430233,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L17OqaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL17OqaU.jpg&h=8e4952ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcqHuCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcqHuCA.jpg&h=d468b84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJ8NFKg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZJ8NFKg.jpg&h=a40663df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pinuT4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpinuT4g.jpg&h=61ad88c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9c528873a14e6c6b61cd30ceaa4cfbb79d51bed","tid":1430233,"uid":237080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:02:53.000Z","msg":"wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cd9241758a40af2adac4594e546861721888b9","tid":1430233,"uid":76181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"同摸奶有咩關係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e1674457a66895ac6702a583bd7ea4b369988f","tid":1430233,"uid":60082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:07:59.000Z","msg":"摸奶圖呢"},{"pid":"73373cfda40